&lt;div data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MailCompose&quot;&gt;We’re a leader in the plastics industry and known for being the “go-to” team for hard-to-find materials and top-notch customer service.&amp;nbsp;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;What We&#39;re Looking For:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for a dependable, hardworking Warehouse Assistant who can support the Warehouse Manager and help keep operations running smoothly.&lt;/p&gt;
