&lt;li data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MailCompose&quot;&gt;Operate forklifts safely and efficiently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MailCompose&quot;&gt;Help receive, stock, and organize incoming inventory&lt;/li&gt;
